Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:27.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:34.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the "Like{\fnGaramond}{\fnNyala}-{\fn}{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:49.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This may sound sudden, but will you enlist with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:55.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're here means you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I don't really get what you—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything you'll be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Erased?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:04.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By God, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:09.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this about enlisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the Like{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the title changes a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:15.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First it was the "Afterlife Battlefront".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:20.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we called it that, it would sound like we're admitting we're dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:22.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we got rid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been changing it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:26.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's the "Like{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, it was the "Don't{\fnNyala}-{\fn}even{\fnNyala}-{\fn}feel{\fnNyala}-{\fn}alive Battlefront".{生きた心地がしゃない戦線}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that name was a total joke, so we changed it the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:33.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a real gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:41.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who comes here reacts like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to be more flexible.{順応性を高めなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:44.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept things as they are.{あるがまま受け止めるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Like{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront's enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.27,0:02:01.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to change the Like{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront name, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:07.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, that's a normal girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You make no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try dying!? {what's the standard TL for the hell girl line?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a joke you'll hear a lot in this world where you can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Was it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:27.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M{\fnNyala}-{\fn}My impressions of your joke aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:32.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I'd probably have a more sensible conversation with her than someone who points guns at girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell me not to aim the gun at her, I won't.{銃を向けるなと言うのなら向けないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the newbie recruitment going?{新人勧誘}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're short on hands, so do whatever it—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:55.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recruitment failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's aiming a gun at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said you were an angel or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:22.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no hospitals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:40.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't get sick here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in on this too!{お前もグルなんだな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:57.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this amnesia is your doing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory loss is quite common when people come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:05.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die in an accident, your head gets damaged, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm already dead, I can't die agai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after that excruciating pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it, but I can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:12.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who disgraced Yurippe and refused to enlist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,H{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of those...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A joke for a world you can't die in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred times! {百篇 hundred times! or ignore this line :P}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:31.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Die die die die die die die die die die die die die die die die die die die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever disgrace Yurippe again, we'll have another dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I guess I was too late for that comeback...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of joke is this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not dying even after going through the pain of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything you'll be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just get erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens I can say goodbye to this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:07.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone I can trust here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, where are the adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can ask the principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:31.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The "You're{\fnNyala}-{\fn}gonna{\fnNyala}-{\fn}die! Battlefront"!{死ぬのはお前だ戦線}{FOTC: "You're Gonna Die! Battlefront"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sound like I'm going to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm talking about that girl. {maybe we should say girl, as Angel isn't very 'woman' looking}{FOTC: I'll go with "girl".}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.28,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're{\fnNyala}-{\fn}gonna{\fnNyala}-{\fn}die! Battlefront. {FOTC: You're Gonna Die! Battlefront}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does feel like I'm going to get killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Flashback Battlefront"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just before you die. {それ死に寸前じゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I{\fnNyala}-{\fn}want{\fnNyala}-{\fn}to{\fnNyala}-{\fn}disappear Battlefront"! {消したい戦線 I want to erase battlefront}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like you're prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Absolute death battlefront"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't absolute death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then about about "Invincible Battle Fleet"?{無敵艦隊}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're no longer a battlefront...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Honorable Defeat Squadron"! {玉砕戦隊}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:04.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to punch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wright Brothers"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to end in "Battlefront"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving way on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the front line in this battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone have a decent suggestion?{もっとましな案はないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that guy's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I got this guy to think about it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's had plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we hear him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The new name for the Like{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}I'm{\fnNyala}-{\fn}dead Battlefront!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do{\fnNyala}-{\fn}whatever{\fnNyala}-{\fn}the{\fnNyala}-{\fn}hell{\fnNyala}-{\fn}you{\fnNyala}-{\fn}want Battlefront".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts to talk back at Yurippe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said do whatever the hell you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:39.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to disappear as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I explained it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be erased without even resisting?{抗いもせず}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you want to become a water flea without even resisting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Water flea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You think souls only reside in human bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow{\fnNyala}-{\fn}minded.{浅はかなり}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:09.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You might become a barnacle or a hermit crab or maybe a sea slater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:15.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face says "I don't have the time to point out that all your examples live in the water".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, there's no particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna go do what Angel says and reincarnate as a barnacle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a barnacle and get eaten by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a good reincarnation for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Barnacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat barnacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them are edible. {FOTC: "edible"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow{\fnNyala}-{\fn}minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:39.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now everyone, don't bully him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... what were we again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Barnacle Battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We, the Barnacle—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're changing it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Afterlife Battlefront!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Battlefront headquarters here is a safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably knew that and tried to take refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I got sent flying the moment I tried to enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that stuff about not necessarily coming back as a human when you're reincarnated...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a joke right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do you know for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Has someone done it to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:18.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Buddhist philosophy says that you might not come back as a person when you're reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... a barnacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:24.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, religion is a human thing to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were still in the world of the living, death was something that came indiscriminately and randomly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there was no way to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you oppose Angel, you'll continue living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was all that back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:47.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to erase Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then take over this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You only just got here, so it can't be helped if you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to be more flexible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept things as they are.{そしてあるがまま受け止めなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And... fight? {FOTC: And... fight?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with us.{FOTC: With us.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast, Yuripp—{早まるな、ゆりっぷ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell for his own trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to enter this room safely you'll need the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Anti{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Angel Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other place we can safely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me a bit of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you do it somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"No God, no Buddha, no Angels".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuri, the leader of this battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:12.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, he's a slob, but every now and then he pulls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make me look good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Matsushita{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:20.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Judo 5th Dan, so everyone calls him Matsushita 5th Dan out of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Oyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He specializes in having absolutely no specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dancing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his way of saying hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We call him TK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of a mysterious guy, and nobody knows his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay working with a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who keeps propping up his glasses to look smart is Takamatsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:46.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Fujimaki{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fujimaki, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the guy who went flying earlier is Noda{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who keeps saying "how shallow{\fnNyala}-{\fn}\N minded" in the shadows is Shiina{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:12:01.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting over here is Iwasawa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, leader of the diversionary squad.{陽動部隊のリーダー}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:06.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a few dozen more members around the school who aren't here at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O... Oto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amnesia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it'll eventually come back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we give him a uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:31.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, why am I in a different uniform from you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:35.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one who's different, it's us who are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the model student uniform.{模範生}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our "Class 3S" uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is a big school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Total student count of over 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mammoth boarding school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it okay to be talking out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as long as it's not about operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been tricked...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:11.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Is that canned coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Key coffee. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:20.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:24.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the middle of club activities or going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did, we'd disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:32.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If us people attend class and join clubs like Angel says, we'd disappear.{天使}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"People"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:37.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost sound like you're saying those aren't people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. They're NPC's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,NPC's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard of that? "Non{\fnNyala}-{\fn}player characters".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:44.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a game now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean they're models that have been here since the start of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So they aren't conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk to them, do they give the same answer every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:58.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably wouldn't be able to figure out the difference between us and them since you just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can converse with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try poking a girl up the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:03.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Up the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll run away or kick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well{\fnNyala}-{\fn}made, aren't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:12.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Also, NPC's don't age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How violent is Angel? {天使の凶暴性は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stabbed as soon as I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that, but that was completely your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:29.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask Angel to prove that you can't die, of course she'd stab you through the heart.{天使}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:35.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For her, that's the same as telling you where the staff room is if you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:39.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Angel obeys the rules of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like she's not good with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea, that's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:49.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's emotionless, blunt, and uses way too few words to be an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not that easy to get kill—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, done in like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:15:01.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone doesn't act like the model students, first she gives a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run away, she follows and intercepts you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:09.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time we do, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are times you get done in like I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't even try acting like the models.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people have disappeared just doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:21.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One more question then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried asking Angel? {天使}{FOTC: Have you tried asking Angel?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:36.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try asking her questions about this world, she has no comment. {FOTC: She doesn't say "No comment", she has "no comment".}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our study meeting ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:48.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully speaking, I haven't actually joined the battlefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want more than anything right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:56.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,is to buy enough time to recover all my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you can shoot as a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it work on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for her legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to chase you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot at a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do her wounds heal quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it out and see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:40.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First off, in order to get you used to things, I'll have you participate in a simple operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is "Operation Tornado".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,T{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Tornado...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to lift meal tickets from the students!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd steal something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not big at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you have so many members and weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare disgrace Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that back.{撤回してもらおうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As members of the Barnacle Extinction Guard Battlefront, {我らフジツボ絶滅保護戦線は}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:10.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we would absolutely never threaten ordinary students with numbers or power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to go extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you'd lift them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, literally lift them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:21.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you're going to be in the "barricade squad" that ties up Angel's movements.{FOTC: "barricade squad"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all surround the main operation point— the dining hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and lie in wait, armed at your specified positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll put you somewhere easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Check with Takamatsu{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun or Oyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun afterwards for the fine details.{FOTC: "Ooyama", "finer details"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm depending on you today too, Iwasawa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you encounter Angel, shoot right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be your signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you hear gunfire from somewhere else, make sure you run to their aid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation commences at 18:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation start!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:14.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How on earth are we supposed to peacefully lift meal tickets with this plan? {FOTC: "lift"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lighting and sound teams on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time.{そろそろ頃合いかと}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fans who've noticed have begun to gather up.{気がついたファンも集ってきています}{FOTC: "begun"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess we'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's GirlDeMo!{Norg: the band name is Girls Dead Monster from wikipedia, wiki also shows the shortening ガルデモ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The concert just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really here, at my position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm the weakest link in this operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally looking down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, shoot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But should I really be shooting at that delicate body?{でも、あんな華奢な体を銃弾でか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll be done in.{(やらなきゃ)やられるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Without mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... I should have hit her legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:06.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard skill: Hand Sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't she stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd target our weakest link?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still only using Hand Sonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her into the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pull back slowly as we attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:20:59.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we were too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:35.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! When are they going to do the lifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only buying time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:39.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it'd be this fierce...{時間稼ぎだ。まさかこんな壮絶なことになるなんて}{FOTC: "fierce"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The act is at its climax. {宴もたけなわだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it on.{回せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it on please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay with that? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:41.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, meat udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:50.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to eat here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't she come after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All we're doing is eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:56.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:03.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this leadership and power, she could make anything happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, she's just eating and living so simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is only one enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're only fighting against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But does that justify those actions?{正当化するのか、その行為を}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too soon to think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:24.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:29.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:18.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Descent...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.29,0:24:19.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.36,0:24:19.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:20.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.36,0:24:21.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you don't understand yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:22.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The trap hasn't been disarmed yet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, damn! I'd forgotten that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:23.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel is getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.40,0:24:23.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You resisted first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:25.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:24.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!!{FOTC: Fire!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:25.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:28.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive that way of living.{FOTC: I can't accept that kind of life.}
